RasterFunctionTemplate.Name: Normalized Difference Built-Up Index (NDBI)
RasterFunctionTemplate.Description: The NDBI index is computed as SWIR(Band6)-NIR(Band05)/ SWIR(Band6)+NIR(Band05) and is suitable for watershed runoff predictions, tracking urbananisation and land-use planning. It highlights urban areas with higher reflectance in the SWIR region, compared to the NIR region.

Function.Name: NDBI
Function.Description: Calculates indexes using the inbuilt formulae or user-defined expression.
